lead_paragraph: Blasting toward the basket, LeBron James didn't break his stride as he flicked away Patty Mills, sending the San Antonio guard sprawling across the floor.

headline.print_headline: LeBron Powers High-Octane Cavs to 117-103 Win Over Spurs
